{"tid":646070,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【直播雙人逃獄】PS4《A Way Out》情願中子彈 唔再執番梘！","createTime":"2018-04-28T17:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T21:19:55.000Z","uid":93870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09afbb9cb7b23764eaeb14726b62fe8a79597e6e","tid":646070,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>按此進入Twitch直播：</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/smilesnooker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fsmilesnooker&d=xzxPzewbXfXB2S0keWFP9ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=427b563f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/smilesnooker</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>深夜 01:00 正式開台！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>《A Way Out》是限定雙人合作的冒險遊戲，玩家可以各自扮演兩名囚犯之一，展開大膽的越獄行動。<br />\n<br />\n本作跳脫以往遊戲的框架，將從一開始的刺激逃獄行動，迅速演變為充滿變數和革命情感的冒險。 <br />\n<br />\n玩家可以操控兩名主角&ndash;里歐 (Leo) 和文森 (Vincent)，為了越獄重獲自由而迫不得已攜手合作。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ne0at5N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fne0at5N.jpg&h=ecfd5330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dpXgAIZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdpXgAIZ.jpg&h=31b50abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rhjzoHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrhjzoHA.jpg&h=bb8f23dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我係Sandy，沙填入臀門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚會同 L仔 巴打一齊逃出生天！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴打入黎邊傾邊睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家踴躍發言！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚，我哋情願中子彈，唔再執番梘！</strong>